# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:11
translate chinese danap2_d3a556ee:

    # pc "Do you have any close family?"
    pc "你有亲近的家人吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:13
translate chinese danap2_61c472dd:

    # cw "I love my family, but I wouldn't say we're close."
    cw "我很爱我的家人，但不能说我们关系很亲密。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:14
translate chinese danap2_48472f67:

    # cw "They all live in Georgia for one, so we don't see each other very often. Just for holidays mostly."
    cw "首先，他们都住在佐治亚州，所以我们很少见面，主要是在节假日才会聚聚。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:15
translate chinese danap2_d74c3d09:

    # cw "And they're all much more conservative and reserved than I am. But I talk to them on the phone when I can."
    cw "而且他们都比我保守得多，也拘谨得多。不过只要有机会，我还是会打电话跟他们聊聊。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:16
translate chinese danap2_2902a9c2:

    # cw "We don't have a whole lot in common to talk about though."
    cw "虽然我们没什么共同话题可聊。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:17
translate chinese danap2_2f9ee344:

    # pc "Any siblings?"
    pc "有兄弟姐妹吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:19
translate chinese danap2_ac8a1be7:

    # cw "I have a younger sister. Mom and Dad had her late, she's only 10."
    cw "我有个妹妹。爸妈生她的时候年纪大了，她才10岁。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:20
translate chinese danap2_99362f9a:

    # pc "Wow, that's a big age difference."
    pc "哇，年龄差真大。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danapersonal2.rpy:22
translate chinese danap2_2af30620:

    # cw "Yeah, but she's great. I love her so much. I wish I could see her more."
    cw "是啊，但她人很好。我特别爱她。真希望能多见见她。"

